<item>
            <title>[LU-4806] Test failure sanity test_53: can not match last_seq/last_id for *OST*-osc-MDT0000</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4806</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Nathaniel Clark &amp;lt;nathaniel.l.clark@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/963b13e0-b144-11e3-808b-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/963b13e0-b144-11e3-808b-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/bcc5032e-b147-11e3-98c2-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/bcc5032e-b147-11e3-98c2-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_53 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;can not match last_seq/last_id for &amp;#42;OST&amp;#42;-osc-MDT0000&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity 53&lt;/p&gt;</description>
